metadata.name: Raius, Winged Beast of Ra
metadata.description:
The rooster crows at the break of dawn
To herald in the new day

The sun then rises in the sky
Bringing light and hope to all

The rooster reminds us that each new day
Is a chance to start anew

And the sun reminds us that
Storms may be present, but hope is always there.

3456 x 4096 px
